title: A Hero's Duty
text: While this objective is undamaged, non-unit cards in your opponent's edge stack lose all Force icons.

title: Luke Skywalker
text:
Edge (1).
This unit gains elite while it is committed to the Force.
Interrupt: When this unit resolves its unit damage icons as a defender, assign the damage to a target enemy unit not participating in the engagement instead.

title: I Will Not Fight You
text:
Play only if you control 1 or more participating units.
Reaction: After an edge battle resolves, your opponent must remove participating units from his side of an engagement until he has an equal (or fewer) number of participating units as you, if able.

title: Search Your Feelings
text:
Play only during an engagement in which you control 1 or more participating units and fewer participating units than your opponent.
Action: Take control of a target participating enemy unit until the end of this engagement. That unit is participating on your side. (Limit 1 per turn.)

title: Secret Objective
text: If you are the attacking player, you may choose an enemy objective that you have not engaged this phase. If you do, you are now engaged with the chosen objective instead.

title: Redeem the Fallen
text: Reaction: After this mission is completed, put a non-Vehicle unit with 4 or fewer printed Force icons into play under your control from your opponent's discard pile.

title: Engineering the Future
text: While this objective is undamaged, exhausted [Rebel Alliance] units you control cannot be dealt damage by enemy combat icons or card effects.

title: General Walex Blissex
text:
Elite.
Action: Focus this unit to remove 1 damage from a [Rebel Alliance] objective. Then, place 1 shield on a [Rebel Alliance] unit or objective. (Limit once per turn.)

title: Overworked Engineer
text: Forced Reaction: After this unit enters play, place 2 focus tokens on it.

title: A-A5 Heavy Speeder Truck
text: Reaction: After you play this unit from your hand, move all focus tokens from all [Rebel Alliance] Character units you control to this unit.

title: Portable Shield Generator
text:
Enhance your play area.
Each ready [Rebel Alliance] unit you control gains: "Protect exhausted [Rebel Alliance] unit."

title: Engineering Brilliance
text: Action: Draw 1 card for each exhausted unit you control.

title: Beyond the Rim
text: While you control 3 or more [Smugglers and Spies] objectives, this objective gains: "Reaction: After your opponent refreshes, remove 1 focus token from a target [Smugglers and Spies] unit you control."

title: Pulsar Skate
text: Action: Discard a [Smugglers and Spies] card from your hand to remove 1 focus token from this unit. (Limit once per turn.)

title: Navigation Droid
text: Protect [Smugglers and Spies] Vehicle unit.

title: Navigation Droid
text: Protect [Smugglers and Spies] Vehicle unit.

title: Smuggler's Hideaway
text:
Enhance your play area.
If you control a [Jedi] or [Rebel Alliance] objective, discard this enhancement from play.

title: Last Ditch Maneuver
text:
Play only during your Force phase.
Action: Focus 2 [Smugglers and Spies] units to shuffle all exhausted units back into their owners' decks.

title: The Emperor's Promise
text: Reaction: After an opponent declares an engagement against an objective not named The Emperor's Promise, deal 1 damage to a target enemy objective.

title: Emperor Palpatine
text:
Elite.
Reaction: After an enemy objective is destroyed, take control of a target enemy unit with 3 or fewer printed Force icons.

title: Emperor's Royal Guard
text: Protect Character. (If a Character unit you control would be damaged, you may place the damage on this unit instead.)

keywords.text: If a Character unit you control would be damaged, you may place the damage on this unit instead.

title: ISB Officer
text: This unit gains [Blast Damage] while there are 1 or more missions in play.

title: Secret Objective
text: If you are the attacking player, you may choose an enemy objective that you have not engaged this phase. If you do, you are now engaged with the chosen objective instead.

title: Lure of the Dark Side
text: Reaction: After this mission is completed, take control of a target unit with 4 or fewer printed Force icons.

title: The Lady's Lesson
text:
Scum and Villainy affiliation only.
To declare an engagement against this objective, the attacking player must declare each unit he controls that is able to be declared.

title: Lady Valarian
text: Reaction: After an opponent's conflict phase ends, deal 1 damage to a target ready unit. If the Balance of the Force is with the dark side, deal 2 damage instead.

title: Whiphid Enforcer
text: This unit gets +1 damage capacity while you control Lady Valarian.

title: Whiphid Enforcer
text: This unit gets +1 damage capacity while you control Lady Valarian.

title: Unrefusable Offer
text: Reaction: After the light side conflict phase begins, target an objective you control. If no engagement is declared against that objective this phase, increase the Death Star dial by 2 at the end of the phase.

title: Vicious Counterattack
text:
Play only during an engagement.
Action: Focus 2 [Scum and Villainy] Character units to destroy each attacking unit.
